      "instruction": "<p>Add 2/3 of your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> to a large bowl (save the rest for garnish!) with your <strong>ground paprika</strong>, <strong>tomato paste, chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>ground sumac</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cider vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add<strong> </strong>a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, and a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>shish taouk marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1687516118355-x200.jpg",
