    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Dice your<strong> tomato[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Add the<strong> shredded lettuce </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>diced tomato</strong>, <strong>remaining ground sumac</strong>,<strong> remaining cider vinegar</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Toss everything together – this is your<strong> sumac salad</strong></p>",
