    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> chicken shish taouk kebabs</strong> with the<strong> sumac salad </strong>and <strong>toasted pitta halves</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle any <strong>remaining juices </strong>from the pan over the chicken and top the salad with the <strong>remaining natural yoghurt</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
